Package org.dockbox.selene.core.events.player

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlayerConnectionEvent
    The abstract type which can be used to listen to all player movement related events.
    PlayerConnectionEvent.PlayerAuthEvent
    The event fired when a remote location is attempting to authenticate to the server.
    PlayerConnectionEvent.PlayerJoinEvent
    The event fired when a player connected to the server.
    PlayerConnectionEvent.PlayerLeaveEvent
    The event fired when a player disconnected from the server.
    PlayerMoveEvent
    The abstract type which can be used to listen to all player movement related events.
    PlayerMoveEvent.PlayerSpawnEvent
    The event fired when a player is teleported to the spawn location.
    PlayerMoveEvent.PlayerSwitchWorldEvent
    The event fired when a player switches to another world.
    PlayerMoveEvent.PlayerTeleportEvent
    The event fired when a player is teleported to another location
    PlayerMoveEvent.PlayerWarpEvent
    The event fired when a player is teleported using a Warp.
